{"tid":1012781,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"（年初四）二條日本妹，邊個靚女D紅D？","createTime":"2019-02-08T00:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T06:23:10.000Z","uid":141988,"like":35,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8803f92db2e1f66ec4816a4f7d3a3a1383163115","tid":1012781,"uid":141988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T00:02:40.000Z","msg":"白麻：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n板野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/08/074737_c3a0e1158914fb6548121c8aaf0686fc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F08%2F074737_c3a0e1158914fb6548121c8aaf0686fc.png&h=8066e33e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n白石麻衣群馬縣出身，是日本偶像藝人、模特兒，女子偶像團體乃木坂46成員。在2011年8月以乃木坂46一期生身分出道，元《Ray》專屬模特與《LARME》常規模特，目前活躍於各大時尚雜誌。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n板野友美，日本女藝人，知名女子偶像團體AKB48前成員，神奈川縣橫濱市出身，隸屬堀製作經紀公司。板野為AKB48的初期創團成員，亦是第一個發行個人單曲的團員。2013年8月27日，自AKB48畢業進行個人演藝活動。"},{"pid":"813767d38286a05b55cd023e128182dc3052ccf4","tid":1012781,"uid":229609,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T00:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都唔屌......"},{"pid":"f1d4c6f363d4501be0c0a3494a3839933520906d","tid":1012781,"uid":49532,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T00:17:15.000Z","msg":"生駒里奈"},{"pid":"5d7e684d12af24deb6eaaf831a59fbd194617669","tid":1012781,"uid":137731,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T00:18:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2279dd013ea9907d03525aff1f07cbb2865fb4b","tid":1012781,"uid":141988,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5d7e684d12af24deb6eaaf831a59fbd194617669","tid":1012781,"uid":137731,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T00:18:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T00:28:46.000Z","msg